parameters: Regarding the Enigma Gate incident.

Recently, there have been multiple incidents of
opening Enigma Gates that connect to the demon
world. It is believed to be the work of the same
culprit, but their whereabouts have not been
determined.

The current situation is not a major problem
because we are able to quickly reseal them, but if
we continue like this, there is a high possibility
that it will become a big problem.

Many soldiers who were believed to have made
contact with the culprit during the search to find
them have gone missing. It is expected that the
culprit has a wide-ranging reconnaissance ability,
and there is a high possibility of an increase in
casualties with a strategy relying solely on
numbers.

We have no choice but to move with personnel who
have enough power to not be killed by the culprit,
but the missing units include squads that can even
defeat Aegis' <Swordsman> alone.

It can be inferred that they have at least a power
stronger than the regular Aegis. Therefore, there
are very few individuals who can pursue them.

We have no choice but to leave it to the current
situation, but it is difficult to find them alone,
so it is considered difficult to resolve. We need
to think of some countermeasures.
